    id: "fortnite-settings-fps",
    title: "Best Fortnite Settings for Maximum FPS in 2026",
    game: "Fortnite",
    category: "Settings",
    excerpt: "Optimize your Fortnite performance with these pro-level settings. Covers video, audio, keybinds, and sensitivity settings used by top competitive players to hit 240+ FPS consistently.",
